Class AddressInfo

  • java.lang.Object

    public class AddressInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<AddressInfo>, java.io.Serializable
    The class AddressInfo creates an AddressInfo object by taking a Name object and address object and constructing them into an AddressInfo object
